msgstr "Hii ni anwani ya kutoka tu. Tafadhali usijibu ujumbe huu."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_acknowledgement/email/body.html:45
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:103
